-- Micex Halts Three-Day Slide as Rusal, Magnitogorsk Advance
-- B y   B r a d   C o o k
-- 2012-03-30T06:15:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-30/micex-halts-three-day-slide-as-rusal-magnitogorsk-advance.html
The Micex Index of 30 Russian
stocks advanced, halting a three-day slide, as commodity prices
climbed. United Co. Rusal, OAO Transneft and OAO  Mechel (MTLR)  all rose
more than 2 percent.  The Micex gained 1.1 percent to 1,511.96 at 10:13 a.m. in
Moscow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
